<subpara id="RM000002XLV05IX_01" type-id="01" category="01">
<s-1 id="RM000002XLV05IX_01_0001" proc-id="RM21Q0EV__00004D400000">
<ptxt>INSTALL COOLER DRYER</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="E184466E01" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
<s2>
<ptxt>Using pliers, install a new cooler dryer to the modulator.</ptxt>
<table>
<title>Text in Illustration</title>
<tgroup cols="2" align="left">
<colspec colname="COL1" colwidth="0.41in"/>
<colspec colname="COL2" colwidth="3.72in"/>
<tbody>
<row>
<entry valign="middle" align="center">
<ptxt>*1</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Modulator</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Apply sufficient compressor oil to a new O-ring and the cap fitting surface.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="E101932" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
<spec>
<title>Compressor oil</title>
<specitem>
<ptxt>ND-OIL 8 or equivalent</ptxt>
</specitem>
</spec>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Using a 14 mm straight hexagon wrench, install a new cap to the cooler condenser core.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="E184465" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
<torque>
<torqueitem>
<t-value1>2.9</t-value1>
<t-value2>30</t-value2>
<t-value3>26</t-value3>
</torqueitem>
</torque>
</s2>
</content1>
</s-1>
<s-1 id="RM000002XLV05IX_01_0003" proc-id="RM21Q0EV__00004D500000">
<ptxt>INSTALL NO. 3 COOLER CONDENSER BRACKET</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>Install the No. 3 cooler condenser bracket with the 2 bolts.</ptxt>
<torque>
<torqueitem>
<t-value1>5.4</t-value1>
<t-value2>55</t-value2>
<t-value3>48</t-value3>
</torqueitem>
</torque>
</s2>
</content1>
</s-1>
<s-1 id="RM000002XLV05IX_01_0004" proc-id="RM21Q0EV__00004D600000">
<ptxt>INSTALL NO. 2 COOLER CONDENSER BRACKET</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>Install the No. 2 cooler condenser bracket with the 2 bolts.</ptxt>
<torque>
<torqueitem>
<t-value1>5.4</t-value1>
<t-value2>55</t-value2>
<t-value3>48</t-value3>
</torqueitem>
</torque>
</s2>
</content1>
</s-1>
<s-1 id="RM000002XLV05IX_01_0005" proc-id="RM21Q0EV__00004D700000">
<ptxt>INSTALL NO. 1 COOLER CONDENSER BRACKET</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<atten4>
<ptxt>Use the same procedure for both No. 1 cooler condenser brackets.</ptxt>
</atten4>
<s2>
<ptxt>Install the No. 1cooler condenser bracket with the 2 bolts.</ptxt>
<torque>
<torqueitem>
<t-value1>3.9</t-value1>
<t-value2>40</t-value2>
<t-value3>35</t-value3>
</torqueitem>
</torque>
</s2>
</content1>
</s-1>
